notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-11T16:23:32.225Z",maintainer-agent,"Scope extension (pm-mpbb ledger lever b, promoted 2026-07-11 when the a22j baseline gate opened): in addition to the once-per-invocation stderr hint in the AC, the mutation/query ENVELOPE must carry the canonical spelling machine-readably when an alias was used (e.g. deprecated_alias + canonical fields), so agents self-migrate programmatically instead of parsing stderr. pm-0mox usage counters are the read side of the same channel. Field naming/placement belongs to the pm-srns uniform envelope spec - coordinate, do not invent a one-off shape here."
